":0,"quote":{"pid":"898dc96bd076251934d6579ba41e35e20c94aa6e","tid":1538641,"uid":273074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:31:34.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 決一不可"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:32:10.000Z","msg":"Sor  缺先岩🙈"},{"pid":"1e9eb2a75611bafb1a787619b9808154debaad09","tid":1538641,"uid":241904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:32:20.000Z","msg":"佢而家撤回根本係想我地8/9少人出黎,咁9/9美國復會就未必過到香港人權關係法<br />\n撤回係3個月前既訴求<br />\n而家係五大訴求,缺一不可<br />\n如果唔係只會每幾年就有一過revolution"},{"pid":"da3c3274966b4fe91c78fb32aca4a02c8f393004","tid":1538641,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:33:13.000Z","msg":"撤你老母咩，條柒頭撤再講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538583\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538583</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n真正港人唔會唔知咩事，點都會繼續出<br />\n唔好再開po講喇，人地都未講撤<br />\n我地就自亂陣腳<br />\n推番行動po啦<br />\n唔好洗走有用資訊<br />\n唔好出冇用既po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73db02bf6a8f8121723ac824770accdde18498a2","tid":1538641,"uid":72800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:34:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong><em><div style=\"text-align: center;\">毋忘七烈 千一義 四眼 三十骨折 手腳筋<br />\n721元朗 811警暴 831車廂 雙肺 一裙<br />\n無數屈辱私刑 重傷昏迷<br />\n<br />\n撤回 定性 釋士 究警 普選</div></em></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港共殺人政權企圖以<strong>錄音、撤回</strong><br />\n轉移<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">太子地鐵傷亡、六警壓脊椎休克昏迷、<br />\n新屋嶺、民主人權法案</span></strong>事件焦點<br />\n醒呀大家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府帶緊風向</span><br />\n背後繼續大清算 入獄 利刑 一年後被失蹤</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">林鄭錄音：事件現時已經上升至「國家主權及國家安全的層次，\n加上世界兩大經濟體前所未有的張力」，她可以做的已經非常少。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><blockquote><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英、美領事館請願 大遊行</span></span></strong><br />\n審視中英聯合聲明 法定性<br />\n中共正統性<br />\n中共毀約 無視國際社會<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">請求國際介入香港前途</span></span></strong> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">施壓制裁港府 還港人雙普選 <br />\n協助制定民主進程</span></span></strong><br />\n香港人道災難 高壓滅聲 白色恐怖 <br />\n執法機器無法無天 受命中共 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">港府管治班子失去自治權 聽命中央</span><br />\n實彈恐怖 威嚇扼殺<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">民主自由</span>現代普世價值<br />\n<strong>人權民主法案 事在必行</strong></blockquote></div>"},{"pid":"1b2f8390257ded5b5cbc24c60194e2309640a390","tid":1538641,"uid":147403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da3c3274966b4fe91c78fb32aca4a02c8f393004","tid":1538641,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:33:13.000Z","msg":"撤你老母咩，條柒頭撤再講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538583\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538583</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n真正港人唔會唔知咩事，點都會繼續出<br />\n唔好再開po講喇，人地都未講撤<br />\n我地就自亂陣腳<br />\n推番行動po啦<br />\n唔好洗走有用資訊<br />\n唔好出冇用既po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:37:11.000Z","msg":"你見我九年都唔出一次就係怕啲風向西玩風向<br />\n依家連登唔係得啲狗mon 啲師奶呀叔都會睇<br />\n所以點都要出下聲"},{"pid":"4b3202e42aff8c5f5a557babe6868de9c5671768","tid":1538641,"uid":147403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:37:51.000Z","msg":"自推 6/10"},{"pid":"1fec490bcdedc432d4c75c4c4ed4f819967091fe","tid":1538641,"uid":147403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:38:05.000Z","msg":"自推 7/10"},{"pid":"3ad2c1babc41a1189dc36eed0193c376832052c5","tid":1538641,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b2f8390257ded5b5cbc24c60194e2309640a390","tid":1538641,"uid":147403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da3c3274966b4fe91c78fb32ac